Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ntu.scse.Order

    public class Order
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Order>
    Represents one hotel Room Service Order that contains information on the item. One RoomService can contain many Orders.
